Class Location

java.lang.Object
se.citerus.dddsample.domain.model.location.Location
All Implemented Interfaces:
DomainEntity<Location>
@Entity(name="Location") public final class Location extends Object implements DomainEntity<Location>
A location is our model is stops on a journey, such as cargo origin or destination, or carrier movement endpoints. It is uniquely identified by a UN Locode.
